hopobject.body: Whereabouts are you from? queens pharmacy opening hours sainsburys berryden Although many more people are taking the West Coast main line, the number of miles they travel seems to be tailing off. Between 2009 and 2010, just after the line was upgraded, passenger miles jumped by 20%. That growth has not been sustained. Between 2011 and 2012 passenger miles increased by 4.6%; between 2012 and 2013 they edged up just 0.9%.
